<i>noun</i>: 추궁 [추궁], 심문 [심문], 신문 [신ː문] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>추궁 [추궁]</dt><br>
<dd>interrogation; close questioning; pressing hard</dd><br>
<dd>잘못한 일을 샅샅이 따져서 밝힘.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of finding out someone's wrongdoing through close questioning.</dd><br>
<dt>심문 [심문]</dt><br>
<dd>interrogation; examination; inquiry</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 사건과 관련된 사람에게 자세하게 따져서 물음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of asking detailed questions to someone related to a certain incident or accident.</dd><br>
<dt>신문 [신ː문]</dt><br>
<dd>1. questioning</dd><br>
<dd>이미 알고 있는 일이 사실인지 거짓인지 확인하기 위하여 캐물음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of questioning inquisitively in order to confirm whether an already known fact is true or false.</dd><br>
<dd>2. interrogation</dd><br>
<dd>정확한 법적 판결을 위해 관계자를 상대로 사건에 대해 캐물으며 조사함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of questioning inquisitively and investigating people concerned regarding a certain incident for an accurate legal decision.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>